values:
Is destiny true? and if it is...are some people ment to be unhappy? can u mess it up? can you ever be completely content with life? Is anyone ever completely happy? Is there love that never loses the freshness of romance? How long does it really take to fall in love? can it really take minutes? hours? days? weeks? 
when you finally get what u have always wanted out of life will you be happy?

why is all of this happening. why did everything have to happen like this...I keep getting hurt over and over again. It NEVER ends. WILL THE HURT AND PAIN EVERRR END?!??! and on top of it all I have people pressuring me from all sides about EVERYTHING. My mind never gets a rest, I need one. I just read an entry from bill on Jen's sn. and it hurt me all over again and I DONT know why??!?!? oh well, some day it will all be gone and life will feel normal and happy again.
